{
  "stem": "14897.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would collect with some of my girlfriends, you know, and I would make up highly romantic, you know, stories about how it would be when we grew up.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In my opinion at the time, sometimes off color, but very naive, naturally.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was a little girl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I loved reading.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I always loved reading, and I do to this time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I played a lot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I played with dolls.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think I was a very imaginative little girl because even I remember playing with dolls, it was not just dressing and undressing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I would always imagine myself on a deserted island, you know, or all kinds of unlikely situations, and make up stories about it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had some very good girlfriends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were close.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We went to parks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We played.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "As I told you, we traveled during the summer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was twice abroad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it just will show you how progressive my father was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In our house, all the ideas came from my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was once in France in 1937 during an international exposition in Paris and twice in then Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I remember that my father insisted that we start going-- I start going to the opera.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so I had seen two operas before the war-- hard, difficult operas, Faust and Eugene Onegin-- poor choices for first operas for a child.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Yeah, so I did a lot of different things as a child.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am very uninterested in sports.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I was teaching here in United States, it took me seven years to find out where the football field was at the high school.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I did swim.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I skated.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I skied as a child.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But, you know, it was not really engaging seriously in sports.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
